android.car.evs

接口 CarEvsManager.CarEvsStreamCallback

  • 封闭类:
    CarEvsManager

    public static interface CarEvsManager.CarEvsStreamCallback
    Application registers #CarEvsStreamCallback object to listen to EVS services' status changes. CarEvsManager supports two client types; one is a System UI type client and another is a normal Android activity type client. The former client type has a priority over the latter type client and CarEvsManager allows only a single client of each type to subscribe.
